overview: The door to hell has opened! Fate is now entrusted to a female Onmyoji... The beautiful girl Kokono Eshino, who was discovered in a CS idol discovery program, makes her full-fledged debut! Co-starring is Eri (Director Takahisa Zeze's "Tokyo x Erotica") and Mao Uehara, a newcomer who stripped for the first time.
title: Woman Onmyoji Imma Impregnation
